9-9184-e2af13b48c41%2Fgenerated-images%2F9c16f3e2-632d-432a-858a-4cac45f62abc.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"book-paper rounded-[1.25rem] border border-line p-5\"><p class=\"display text-2xl font-bold\">Not Sleepy Yet</p><p class=\"mt-3 line-clamp-6 text-sm leading-6 text-ink/72\">Aurelia was NOT sleepy. Not even a little bit.\n\nShe stood in her favorite yellow dress and her rainbow rainboots. Her brown hair tumbled past her shoulders, curling at the tips, half of it flopping right over one eye the way it always did.\n\nShe bounced on her toes. She wiggled her fingers. She made a silly face at her stuffed bunny.\n\n&quot;Bedtime, sweet girl!&quot; Mama called from the doorway.\n\nAurelia&#x27;s big blue-grey eyes went wide. Her mouth stretched into the biggest grin you ever saw, the kind that showed her one special dimple on her right cheek.\n\n&quot;But Mama,&quot; she said, &quot;I can&#x27;t go to bed yet!&quot;</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"border-y border-line bg-card/68 py-16\"><div class=\"page-shell\"><h2 class=\"display text-4xl font-bold\">More than a name in a template</h2><div class=\"mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-cream p-6 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles h-6 w-6 text-honey\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg><p class=\"mt-5 font-bold leading-7\">Story details shaped around your child</p></div><div 