ding-6 text-ink/70\">A complete 10-chapter storybook: 2 text pages and 2 illustrations per chapter (20 illustrations total), plus a title page, dedication page, opening note, and back matter with discussion questions and a draw-along prompt. Delivered as a PDF.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">What illustration styles are available?</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-ink/70\">You can choose any style in the creation form: warm watercolor, soft painterly, classic children’s book, cute cartoon, whimsical fantasy, gentle woodland, bright colorful modern, minimal simple shapes, or Ghibli-inspired cozy. The style you choose is applied consistently across all 20 illustrations.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">How much does a book cost?</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-ink/70\">Pricing is set at checkout. There are no subscriptions — you pay once per book. A price range will be listed here when launch pricing is confirmed.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">What age range is PageCub for?</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-ink/70\">PageCub stories are written for children roughly ages 3–12. You can specify your child&#x27;s age in the creation form and the story length and vocabulary will be shaped accordingly.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">Can I preview the finished book?</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-ink/70\">Yes. You can read the full finished book digitally before ordering any printed copy.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"page-shell pb-16\"><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] bg-ink px-8 py-12 text-center text-white shadow-soft\"><h2 class=\"display text-4xl font-bold\">Ready to make their story?</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-white/75\">Start with a